body:
reverts this commit, https://github.com/airbnb/superset/pull/2597
which prevented multiple filters from working on dashboards

@mistercrunch

Bumping `eslint-config-airbnb` from 9.x to 14.x brought in a lot of linting issues, many of which I switched off in `.eslintrc` for the sake of moving forward.

We can go back and look at the list of blacklisted rules and decide which ones we want to tackle in individual PRs.

@ascott
